data.text:
Elden and Roberta Taylor of Canton celebrated their 66th anniversary with numerous events with family and friends. The former Bobby Evans and her husband were married on March 9, 1945, at First Christian Church in North Industry. They attend Mount Zion Community Church in Canton.

They are the parents of Dr. Melanie Taylor of Whittier, Calif., and Howard and Jill Taylor of Canton. The couple have seven grandchildren and three great-grandchildren.

Elden is retired from The Timken Co., where he worked as a millwright supervisor. Bobby is retired from Canton Local School District, where she worked as cafeteria

manager.
